<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Stands are not primarily disturbed by fire, but they may be susceptible to high-intensity fires. <i>Morella californica </i>is fire resistant, as it sprouts readily after fire from its root crown (Howell 1970, Holzman and Folger 2003).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
